### Resume Screener API — Test Requests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or similar

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### List all resumes
GET {{baseUrl}}/resume

### Upload a resume (use a real PDF/DOCX file)
# POST {{baseUrl}}/resume/upload
# Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary
# ------boundary
# Content-Disposition: form-data; name="resume"; filename="test.pdf"
# Content-Type: application/pdf
# < ./test-resume.pdf
# ------boundary--

### Analyze a specific resume (replace with real ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/resume/analyze/REPLACE_WITH_RESUME_ID
Content-Type: application/json

### Get resume details
GET {{baseUrl}}/resume/REPLACE_WITH_RESUME_ID

### Get job recommendations
POST {{baseUrl}}/jobs/recommend/REPLACE_WITH_RESUME_ID
Content-Type: application/json

### Get stored recommendations
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs/REPLACE_WITH_RESUME_ID
